===Noun===
# sci-fi term to refer to a communication device that enables users to [[instantaneously]] communicate; [[faster-than-light]] communication device;

====Etymology====
First attested in 1974 in [[w:The Dispossessed|The Dispossessed]] by [[w:Ursula K. Le Guin|Ursula K. Le Guin]]. Le Guin herself states that she derived it from ''[[answerable]]''.

